   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support Rural Schools in Sri Lanka</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will support rural schools from the poorest sections in Sri Lanka to get their basic requirements such as sports goods; library books; musical instruments; water, sanitation &amp; hygiene requirements; and essential school packs comprising of school supplies, bags, shoes, etc., for each student. Our assistance will help them surmount the hurdle of poverty to reach their educational goals thus ensuring a brighter future and the opportunity of breaking the cycle of poverty.</narrative>
